Feature: Removing Groups
In order to Remove a Group in an Organization
As a Administrator
I need to open an Index page and do some operations
@orggrpremove
Scenario: Removing Groups under Organization
	Given Navigate to Groups Page
	When I click on Org Menu Bar 
	And click on View Group Under Organization sub Menu
	And I choose an Organization
	Then I should see the organization id organization name groupid groupname Action
	When I click on remove link button
	Then the selected group is removed
